tva:BasicDescription.tva:Title: We Are Never Ever Getting Back Together by Taylor Swift (Alexa Goddard Cover)
tva:BasicDescription.tva:Synopsis: It's been a while since I uploaded a video, but here's my first Taylor Swift cover - my own acoustic version of 'We Are Never Ever Getting Back Together'. I hope you like it! Please comment, share with your friends on Facebook and Twitter and subscribe to my channel (www.youtube.com/AlexaMusicTV) -- and let me know what you think on twitter www.twitter.com/AlexaGoddard, tweet me with #AlexaNeverCover Thanks to Dani B for his guitar skills in this video too -- you can check his channel over at www.youtube.com/DaniBOfficial. Please comment, subscribe and join me on all your social networks! Twitter: @alexagoddard // www.facebook.com/alexagoddard // www.alexagoddard.com
